WEBVTT

00:02:59.596 --> 00:03:02.137
and the moray will understand that signal.

00:03:02.816 --> 00:03:05.793
The moray may go into the crevice
and get the fish,

00:03:05.817 --> 00:03:08.475
but the fish may bolt
and the grouper may get it.

00:03:08.880 --> 00:03:14.911
This is an ancient partnership that we
have just recently found out about.

00:03:14.935 --> 00:03:18.020
How do we celebrate
that ancient partnership?

00:03:18.044 --> 00:03:19.622
Mostly fried.

00:03:20.918 --> 00:03:24.518
A pattern is emerging and it says
a lot more about us

00:03:24.542 --> 00:03:26.702
than it does about them.

00:03:27.610 --> 00:03:30.015
Sea otters use tools